<TITLE> Monindra Lal Chakma gets bail </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Khagrachari, Nov 16 (bdnews24.com)  Khagrachhari District Council chairman Monindra Lal Tripura secured bail on Sunday. Khagrachhari district judge Mohammad Mostofa Ahmed granted him bail on a bond of Tk 30,000. Advocate Ripol Chakma, the laweer for Monindra who is now in Dhaka Central Jail, said he would be released once the jail authorities received the bail documents. On Oct. 31, police detained him from Tejgaon in the capital. Later, he was shown arrested in Anupam Tripura murder case. The other accused persons in the caseParen Tripura, Shanti Bikash Chakma, Mosharraf Hossain, Kolnath Tripura and Awal Gaziare have been detained in the Khagrachhari district jail. bdnews
